{"tid":2418286,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿婆路邊撿紙箱遇狂風吹散　黑衣暖男經過下車救援…一看是王嘉爾","createTime":"2021-02-22T13:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T15:02:57.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc56119b99cf73e9048701500b0e1effd517ac8","tid":2418286,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"JYP娛樂旗下當家男團GOT7在1月底時，透過公司發表聲明「雙方為了祈願新的未來，在協議下決定不續約」，團員們以單飛不解散的方式各奔東西，其中王嘉爾（Jackson）加入經紀公司SUBLIME，與Rain、宋康昊成為一家人，而個性熱心助人的他22又被網友曝光一段暖心的善舉，引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5466/5466094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5466%2F5466094.jpg&h=c4d7ef2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾私底下有著細心溫暖的個性，深受許多粉絲喜愛。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／jacksonwang852g7）<br />\n<br />\n王嘉爾在鏡頭前總是呈現人來瘋的形象，但是私底下的他卻是一個細心的暖男，22日有一名泰國網友就在推特上傳，一段在2016年於首爾街頭巧遇他的故事，網友透露當時自己正走在江南的狎鷗亭街頭，看到路邊一位白髮奶奶正在撿紙箱，怎料突然吹起了一陣大風，雙手無力的奶奶只能看著紙箱隨風飄走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5466/5466091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5466%2F5466091.jpg&h=8c37e149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友路上看到老奶奶撿的紙箱被吹走，一名黑衣男下車幫忙。（圖／翻攝自推特／@whatdoyoudoink1）<br />\n<br />\n這時，網友看到一個穿著全黑的潮男從一輛黑色廂型車下來，直直走向無助的老奶奶，幫忙把紙箱全部撿起，直到搜集好全部的紙箱，成功交給奶奶才轉身離去，男子一轉頭該名網友才發現，男方的真實身分原來是GOT7的成員王嘉爾，而在網友捕捉到的兩張照片中，可以看出奶奶得到王嘉爾的幫助，笑得非常開心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5466/5466092.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5466%2F5466092.jpg&h=02b8e6aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友在路邊巧遇王嘉爾，親眼目睹他下車幫助撿紙箱的老奶奶。（圖／翻攝自推特／@whatdoyoudoink1）<br />\n<br />\n而王嘉爾這段2016年暖舉被曝光後，也吸引了大批網友的迴響，紛紛留言表示「Jackson一直以來都這麼溫暖」、「願意特地下車幫忙，真的很不簡單」、「看到奶奶的笑容怎麼有點催淚」、「果然沒有喜歡錯人」，引起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5466/5466093.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5466%2F5466093.jpg&h=ce12e634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾暖舉曝光，引起大批網友狂讚。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／jacksonwang852g7）<br />\n<br />\nJYP DADDY將最後既人性光輝教晒JACKSON。。。"},{"pid":"9bb8094ff0bd92c9cd2ce17ba36f9b5b07211b81","tid":2418286,"uid":258899,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"又咁啱比佢即刻影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baad92c041d7dc628dcd40c0e8c63a42074966d5","tid":2418286,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:22:38.000Z","msg":"負皮個個D人忍住忍住"},{"pid":"f2e5570aec14d05c490cc7daa78a2ea2e4a4098b","tid":2418286,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"反嘉爾=黑心🖤"},{"pid":"25e26e6a22868b33ec0c41de170806cdc2719cf4","tid":2418286,"uid":87394,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9bb8094ff0bd92c9cd2ce17ba36f9b5b07211b81","tid":2418286,"uid":258899,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"又咁啱比佢即刻影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"邊有咁岩呢次就比人影到<br />\n應該平時都做唔少 真男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95887b8f3661ec400d32b3326baf09fbfaffdd0","tid":2418286,"uid":137569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKAmwc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKAmwc8.jpg&h=23082e4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcba8bfb1df9ec85f326a72bc72584d02806a504","tid":2418286,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95887b8f3661ec400d32b3326baf09fbfaffdd0","tid":2418286,"uid":137569,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKAmwc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmK